name: Pretty Heart Wall Decoration
description:
An original piece of wall art/decoration, and a real labour of 'love!' 

The piece consists of 12 flowers which I individually crafted out of some old map paper (an old UK road atlas!) and set against a cream background. 

The piece comes in a white square box frame: 14 x 14 x 1 inches, and would fit well in most spaces. It has a hook on the back so it can be wall-mounted, but it would look equally good propped-up on a shelf or mantle-piece! 

I will package the piece securely using plenty of bubble-wrap to ensure safe arrival! 

*PLEASE ALLOW 3-5 DAYS FOR DELIVERY - NO SIGNATURE REQUIRED*
